David Dukes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Dukes 0 David Coleman Dukes (June 6, 1945 – October 9, 2000) was an American character actor. He had a long career in films, appearing in 35. Dukes starred in the mini-series The Winds of War and War and Remembrance in the 1980s, and he was a frequent television guest star. Later in life, Dukes had recurring roles on shows such as Pauly, Sisters and Dawson's Creek. David_Coleman_Dukes ( June_6_,_1945 – October_9_,_2000 ) was an_American_character_actor .
